text: Josip Kujundžić (born 1916, date of death unknown) was a Yugoslav gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1916 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Yugoslav male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Yugoslavia Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
